Instead, you put Nginx (or Apache, Caddy, Traefik) in front:Nginx handles:SSL/TLS certificates (HTTPS via Letâs Encrypt).Rate limiting, load balancing, caching.Forwarding requests to Uvicorn on port 8000.Example Nginx config:
